how’s seminal date. You can see them below.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1240\" height=\"1837\" src=\"https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/the-last-of-us-season-2-art-ellie.jpg?w=650\" alt=\"the last of us season 2\" srcset=\"https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/the-last-of-us-season-2-art-ellie.jpg 1240w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/the-last-of-us-season-2-art-ellie.jpg?resize=135,200 135w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/the-last-of-us-season-2-art-ellie.jpg?resize=203,300 203w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/the-last-of-us-season-2-art-ellie.jpg?resize=768,1138 768w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/the-last-of-us-season-2-art-ellie.jpg?resize=691,1024 691w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/the-last-of-us-season-2-art-ellie.jpg?resize=1037,1536 1037w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/the-last-of-us-season-2-art-ellie.jpg?resize=68,100 68w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/the-last-of-us-season-2-art-ellie.jpg?resize=600,889 600w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/the-last-of-us-season-2-art-ellie.jpg?resize=126,187 126w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/the-last-of-us-season-2-art-ellie.jpg?resize=1000,1481 1000w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/the-last-of-us-season-2-art-ellie.jpg?resize=244,361 244w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/the-last-of-us-season-2-art-ellie.jpg?resize=783,1160 783w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/the-last-of-us-season-2-art-ellie.jpg?resize=64,95 64w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/the-last-of-us-season-2-art-ellie.jpg?resize=27,40 27w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/the-last-of-us-season-2-art-ellie.jpg?resize=162,240 162w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/the-last-of-us-season-2-art-ellie.jpg?resize=324,480 324w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/the-last-of-us-season-2-art-ellie.jpg?resize=648,960 648w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/the-last-of-us-season-2-art-ellie.jpg?resize=253,375 253w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/the-last-of-us-season-2-art-ellie.jpg?resize=506,750 506w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/the-last-of-us-season-2-art-ellie.jpg?resize=1013,1500 1013w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/the-last-of-us-season-2-art-ellie.jpg?resize=152,225 152w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/the-last-of-us-season-2-art-ellie.jpg?resize=304,450 304w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/the-last-of-us-season-2-art-ellie.jpg?resize=608,900 608w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/the-last-of-us-season-2-art-ellie.jpg?resize=405,600 405w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/the-last-of-us-season-2-art-ellie.jpg?resize=810,1200 810w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/the-last-of-us-season-2-art-ellie.jpg?resize=113,168 113w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/the-last-of-us-season-2-art-ellie.jpg?resize=227,337 227w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/the-last-of-us-season-2-art-ellie.jpg?resize=456,675 456w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/the-last-of-us-season-2-art-ellie.jpg?resize=1139,1687 1139w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/the-last-of-us-season-2-art-ellie.jpg?resize=270,400 270w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/the-last-of-us-season-2-art-ellie.jpg?resize=540,800 540w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/the-last-of-us-season-2-art-ellie.jpg?resize=1080,1600 1080w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/the-last-of-us-season-2-art-ellie.jpg?resize=101,150 101w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/the-last-of-us-season-2-art-ellie.jpg?resize=300,444 300w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/the-last-of-us-season-2-art-ellie.jpg?resize=1200,1778 1200w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/the-last-of-us-season-2-art-ellie.jpg?resize=150,222 150w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/the-last-of-us-season-2-art-ellie.jpg?resize=110,163 110w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/the-last-of-us-season-2-art-ellie.jpg?resize=285,422 285w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/the-last-of-us-season-2-art-ellie.jpg?resize=320,474 320w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/the-last-of-us-season-2-art-ellie.jpg?resize=640,948 640w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/the-last-of-us-season-2-art-ellie.jpg?resize=800,1185 800w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/the-last-of-us-season-2-art-ellie.jpg?resize=518,768 518w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/the-last-of-us-season-2-art-ellie.jpg?resize=1024,1517 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1240px) 100vw, 1240px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eIn August, HBO released the first footage from the show’s sophomore run via a Max promo. In it, Joel made an expected confession — to an unexpected character: \u003ca href=\"https://tvline.com/casting-news/catherine-ohara-the-last-of-us-season-2-cast-character-role-1235141672/\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eSeason 2 newbie Catherine O’Hara\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/a\u003e (\u003cem\u003eSchitt’s Creek\u003c/em\u003e). She presumably wondered about Ellie, asking Joel, “Did you hurt her?” His response: “I saved her.” Fans of the franchise will recognize this as a deviation from the original story. In the video game, Joel delivers his confession to his brother Tommy (and only Tommy).\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eThe previous teaser (seen below) seemed to indicate more changes from the Naughty Dog video game’s storyline. We were also intrigued by what’s going on around the :45 mark; those who know \u003cem\u003eThe Last of Us Part II\u003c/em\u003e inside and out will recognize this scene as something that is shown at the very end of that game. Given that series creators Craig Mazin and Neil Druckmann have indicated that the show will likely go at least three seasons, it’s interesting that the moment is included in Season 2.\n\n\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cp\u003e\n\u003ciframe loading=\"lazy\" title=\"The Last of Us Season 2 | The Last of Us Day Official Teaser | Max\" width=\"350\" height=\"197\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/BOsAJ7oe2QE?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" referrerpolicy=\"strict-origin-when-cross-origin\" allowfullscreen=\"\"\u003e\u003c/iframe\u003e\n\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eAlso of note: Isaac (\u003cem\u003eWestworld\u003c/em\u003e’s Jeffrey Wright) and a captured Seraphite, some longing looks between Ellie and Dina, and the music at the start of the clip, which is from a series of poignant moments in \u003cem\u003ePart II\u003c/em\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1240\" height=\"1837\" src=\"https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/the-last-of-us-season-2-art-joel.jpg?w=650\" alt=\"the last of us season 2\" srcset=\"https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/the-last-of-us-season-2-art-joel.jpg 1240w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/the-last-of-us-season-2-art-joel.jpg?resize=135,200 135w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/the-last-of-us-season-2-art-joel.jpg?resize=203,300 203w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/the-last-of-us-season-2-art-joel.jpg?resize=768,1138 768w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/the-last-of-us-season-2-art-joel.jpg?resize=691,1024 691w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/the-last-of-us-season-2-art-joel.jpg?resize=1037,1536 1037w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/the-last-of-us-season-2-art-joel.jpg?resize=68,100 68w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/the-last-of-us-season-2-